<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6626827>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Holotype of Rhinella unapensis sp. nov. (CRBIIAP-2125); A) dorsal view; B) ventral view; C) lateral view of head; D) dorsal view of head; E) ventral view of right hand; F) ventral view of right foot." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6626827/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6626829>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Type series and morphological variation in preserved specimens of Rhinella unapensis sp. nov. A–C= CRBIIAP- 2114 (adult female); D–F=MZUNAP-AN 540 (adult male); G–I= CRBIIAP-2115 (adult female); J–L= CRBIIAP-2123 (adult male)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6626829/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6626831>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Morphological variation of living specimens of Rhinella unapensis sp. nov. A–D= Puerto Almendra locality; E–H= Allpahuayo Mishana Natural Reserve." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6626831/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6626823>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Distribution map of the two new species described herein. Rhinella angeli sp. nov. Yellow color: 1) Nueva Esperanza; 2) Panguana; 3) Mircillo; 4) Sacacaca; 5) Cauchuyo; 6) Corrientes; 7) Taguado; 8) Sierra del Divisor National Reserve; 9) Matsés National Reserve. R. unapensis sp. nov. Red color: 1) Puerto Almendra; 2) Fundo UNAP; 3) Iquitos-Nauta Highway 70 km. Stars indicate the type locality." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6626823/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6626833>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. A= Habitat of Rhinella unapensis sp. nov. B–C= R. unapensis sp. nov. resting in leaves and stems of low shrubs (~1.20 m)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6626833/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

